'''小羅伯特·柯林頓·理查森'''（{{lang-en|Robert Clinton Richardson, Jr.}}，{{bd|1935年|8月19日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的二壘手。12年職業生涯皆效力於紐約洋基。他與[[湯尼·庫貝克|湯尼·庫貝克]]以及{{link-en|克萊特·博耶|Clete Boyer}}組成了洋基隊在1950年代末至1960年代初的黃金內野陣容。1960年世界大賽，他被選為世界大賽MVP，成為了史上唯一一位拿下世界大賽MVP的亞軍球隊成員。1962年，他以單季209支安打拿下美聯安打王頭銜。

1976年，理查森曾代表共和黨參選眾議院代表，不過最後沒能選上。
==職業生涯==
===1953年–1956年：初出茅廬===
1953年，理查森從1B聯盟（Class B）開始職棒生涯。<ref name="SABR">{{cite web|last=Pasculli|first=Len|url=https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/47363efd|title=Bobby Richardson|work=SABR|accessdate=2020-04-09|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413025048/https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/47363efd|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在那裡的打擊率只有2成11，因此球隊將他降到更低的1D聯盟（Class D）。<ref name="SABR"/><ref name="minors">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=richar007rob|title=Bobby Richardson Minor League Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425012208/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=richar007rob|dead-url=no}}</ref>

理查森在1D的打擊率高達4成12，他也在1954年被升上1A。而他也在那年以3成10打擊率與171支安打拿下1A聯盟的MVP大獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=af825f91|title=1954 Eastern League Batting Leaders|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-09|archive-date=2015-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151230142521/http://www.baseball-reference.com/register/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=af825f91|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1955年，理查森先從3A開季。<ref>{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|page=31|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1955/04/01/85690101.html?pageNumber=31|title=Five Players Cut From Squad Before Yanks Start Northward|work=The New York Times|date=1955-04-01|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141400/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1955/04/01/85690101.html?pageNumber=31|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於[[吉爾·麥克道高德|吉爾·麥克道高德]]在某次打擊練習被平飛球擊中受傷，因此洋基將年僅19歲的理查森拉上大聯盟。<ref name="SABR"/>他在初登板面對名人堂投手[[吉姆·邦寧|吉姆·邦寧]]便敲出大聯盟首安，<ref name="SABR"/>之後他在出賽3場比賽後被下放到3A。<ref name="1955 Richardson"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Drebinger|first=John|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1955/08/16/79451253.html?pageNumber=26|title=Home Runs Mark 5–4, 12–6 Triumphs|work=The New York Times|date=1955-08-16|accessdate=2020-04-10|page=26|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141401/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1955/08/16/79451253.html?pageNumber=26|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月他又回到大聯盟，並出賽了4場比賽。<ref name="1955 Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1955|title=Bobby Richardson 1955 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194859/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1955|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1956年，理查森進入了洋基隊的開幕戰先發名單。不過那年他僅出賽5場比賽，打擊率只有1成43。<ref>{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|page=42|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1956/05/14/93203323.html?pageNumber=42|title=Bombers Win, 11–2; Drop 5–1 Decision|work=The New York Times|date=1956-05-14|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109103949/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1956/05/14/93203323.html?pageNumber=42|dead-url=no}}</ref>結果回到小聯盟的他又找回了打擊手感，多項數據都在聯盟名列前茅。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=62cbeec8|title=1956 American Association Batting Leaders|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141402/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=62cbeec8|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===1957年–1959年：站穩大聯盟===
1957年，理查森表現大幅進步，加上原本的二壘手[[比利·馬丁|比利·馬丁]]在春訓期間與[[米奇·曼托|米奇·曼托]]發生駕駛高爾夫球車相撞事故受傷，所以他成功接替馬丁成為球隊的主力二壘手。<ref name="Silence">{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|page=34|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/06/25/84738480.html?pageNumber=34|title=Silence! Bobby Richardson at Work|work=The New York Times|date=1957-06-25|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141402/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/06/25/84738480.html?pageNumber=34|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Golenbock|first=Peter|origyear=1994|title=Wild, High and Tight: The Life and Death of Billy Martin|publisher=Antenna Books|edition=Kindle version of Antenna Books ebook |page=2631–2644 |location=New York|year=2014|isbn=978-1-62306-022-0|ref={{sfnRef|Golenbock}}}}</ref>雖然總教練{{link-en|卡西·史丹格爾|Casey Stangel}}曾說道：「理查森不菸不酒、不嚼口香糖、生活自律，但是打擊率也從未超過2成50。」<ref name="SABR"/>不過其實理查森在1957年上半季曾締造3成31的打擊率，並入選了第一次的明星賽。<ref name="Silence"/>然而他在下半季的打擊率下滑，最終整年的打擊率為2成56。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1957|title=Bobby Richardson 1957 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194908/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1957|dead-url=no}}</ref>

同年9月，理查森的二壘手大位被老將{{link-en|傑瑞·柯爾曼|Jerry Coleman}}取代。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=colemje01&t=b&year=1957|title=Jerry Coleman 1957 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141403/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=colemje01&t=b&year=1957|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時總教練正苦惱要選擇哪一位球員做為世界大賽的先發二壘手，最終他選擇了柯爾曼。<ref>{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/10/01/91165032.html?pageNumber=54|title=Mantle's Status Remains in Doubt|work=The New York Times|date=1957-10-01|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109102720/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/10/01/91165032.html?pageNumber=54|dead-url=no}}</ref>理查森在世界大賽淪為代打或是後半段防守的角色，<ref name="reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/richabo01.shtml|title=Bobby Richardson Stats|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-09|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410130018/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/richabo01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Postseason Coleman">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=colemje01&t=b&year=0&post=1|title=Jerry Coleman Postseason Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141424/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=colemje01&t=b&year=0&post=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>而洋基在那年以3勝4敗輸給勇士，無緣拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref name="Postseason Coleman"/>

隨著柯爾曼在球季結束後退休，理查森再次成為球隊的主力二壘手。<ref>{{cite web|last=McGowen|first=Roscoe|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/11/22/90856130.html?pageNumber=38|page=38|title=Coleman Retires as Player After Nine Years with Yankees|work=The New York Times|date=1957-11-22|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109104014/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/11/22/90856130.html?pageNumber=38|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而他在前18場比賽只繳出2成03的打擊率，於是洋基將二壘位置交給傷癒復出的麥克道高德，理查森成為了替補選手。<ref name="1958 Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1958|title=Bobby Richardson 1958 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194912/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1958|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=mcdougi01&t=b&year=1958|title=Gil McDougald 1958 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611200731/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=mcdougi01&t=b&year=1958|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時理查森曾因為表現不佳一度考慮離開棒球界，不過最後被洋基總經理{{link-en|雷夫·霍克|Ralph Houk}}說服留下。<ref name="SABR"/>這年的世界大賽，理查森出賽4場比賽並有一次先發，<ref name="Postseason Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=0&post=1|title=Bobby Richardson Postseason Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194855/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=0&post=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA195810050.shtml|title=1958 World Series Game 4, Braves at Yankees, October 5|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521055350/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA195810050.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然他沒有擊出任何安打，不過洋基最終還是順利奪冠。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>

1959年，洋基隊任命理查森擔任游擊手。<ref name="Kiely">{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/04/20/89183045.html?pageNumber=37|title=Kiely Is Credited with 5–4 Victory|work=The New York Times|page=37|date=1959-04-20|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141426/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/04/20/89183045.html?pageNumber=37|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過隨著麥克道高德再次受傷，理查森又回到了二壘手的位置。<ref name="Kiely"/><ref name="1959 Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1959|title=Bobby Richardson 1959 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|access-date=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194917/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1959|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於他在前20場比賽的打擊率只有2成32，因此洋基選擇讓[[湯尼·庫貝克|湯尼·庫貝克]]擔任先發二壘手。<ref name="1959 Richardson"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=kubekto01&t=b&year=1959|title=Tony Kubek 1959 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428014200/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=kubekto01&t=b&year=1959|dead-url=no}}</ref>

時任洋基打擊教練的[[比爾·狄奇|比爾·狄奇]]發現理查森表現起伏不定，於是決定好好改造這名球員。他先讓理查森拿著更重的球棒嘗試揮棒。<ref name="SABR"/>而理查森也成功讓自己的打擊率上升至3成，並入選第二次的明星賽。<ref name="1959 Richardson"/><ref name="1959 Richardson"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Becker|first=Bill|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/08/03/88805148.html?pageNumber=31|title=Walker and Drysdale Expected to Start in Second All-Star Game|work=The New York TImes|page=31|date=1959-08-03|accessdate=2020-04-17|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109105119/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/08/03/88805148.html?pageNumber=31|dead-url=no}}</ref>1959年7月25日，理查森終於敲出生涯首轟，而另一名洋基新秀{{link-en|弗里茨·布里克爾|Fritz Brickell}}也在同天敲出生涯首轟。<ref>{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/07/26/110087361.html?pageNumber=166|page=166|title=Homer Is Decisive|work=The New York Times|date=1959-07-26|accessdate=2020-04-11|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141431/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1959/07/26/110087361.html?pageNumber=166|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時理查森是洋基隊唯一一位能夠挑戰單季3成打擊率的球員，他在球季最後一場比賽敲出3支安打，最終打擊率為3成01。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1959-batting-leaders.shtml|title=1959 AL Batting Leaders|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527045607/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1959-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他也敲出2轟與33分打點，<ref name="reference"/><ref name="Shared Hero">{{cite web|last=Effrat|first=Louis|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1960/10/09/99878556.html?pageNumber=276|page=276|title=Batting in 6 Runs, He Shares Role of Hero With Ford|work=The New York Times|date=1960-10-09|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141438/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1960/10/09/99878556.html?pageNumber=276|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後他在MVP票選中拿下第18名。<ref name="reference"/>
===1960年–1962年：連續的世界大賽===
1960年，理查森已經逐漸成為洋基隊上的不動二壘手。<ref name="1960 Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1960|title=Bobby Richardson 1960 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194922/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1960|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他還三度達成單場敲出3支安打的表現。<ref name="1960 Richardson"/>4月30日，他敲出了他該年唯一一支全壘打。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL196004300.shtml|title=New York Yankees at Baltimore Orioles Box Score, April 30, 1960|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519015151/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL196004300.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月6日，他在面對運動家的比賽中跑回致勝分。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196005060.shtml|title=Kansas City Athletics at New York Yankees Box Score, May 6, 1960|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521055916/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196005060.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他的打擊率為2成52，並打回26分打點。<ref name="reference"/>

[[1960年世界大賽|1960年世界大賽]]，理查森在第二場比賽敲出3支安打。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>第三場，他在滿壘時上場打擊。<ref>{{cite web|last=Terrell|first=Roy|url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1960/10/17/the-knife-and-the-hammer|title=The Knife and the Hammer|work=Sports Illustrated|date=1960-10-17|accessdate=2020-04-17|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141431/https://vault.si.com/vault/1960/10/17/the-knife-and-the-hammer|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時三壘指導教練給了他短打的暗號，不過在投手取得兩好球後，理查森決定正面對決，<ref name="SABR"/>他耐心選球取得滿球數，接著敲出一支滿貫砲。後來他又在第4局敲出2分打點的安打，他單場6分打點也刷新了世界大賽單一球員的單場打點紀錄。<ref name="SABR"/>第4場他又敲出2支安打，不過最後洋基一分惜敗。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>第6場，他敲出了兩支三壘安打。<ref name="SABR"/><ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>他還在第7場比賽的9局上跑回追平分，不過最後海盜隊靠著[[比爾·馬澤羅斯基|比爾·馬澤羅斯基]]的再見全壘打拿下勝利。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxsports.com/mlb/story/world-series-history-bill-mazeroski-s-home-run-to-win-1960-world-series-100616|title=World Series History: Bill Mazeroski’s Home Run to Win 1960 World Series|work=Fox Sports|date=2017-06-30|accessdate=2020-04-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PIT/PIT196010130.shtml|title=1960 World Series Game 7, Yankees at Pirates, October 13|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-17|archive-date=2018-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014053104/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PIT/PIT196010130.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而理查森在這個系列賽繳出3成67打擊率與12分打點的紀錄，<ref name="SABR"/><ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>因此他依舊被選為世界大賽的MVP。他也成為大聯盟唯一一個被選為世界大賽MVP，該年卻沒贏下冠軍的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://baseball-almanac.com/awards/aw_mvpw.shtml|title=World Series Most Valuable Player Award|work=Baseball Almanac|accessdate=2020-04-09|archive-date=2020-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113092851/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/aw_mvpw.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他還獲贈一台雪佛蘭跑車，以獎勵他在世界大賽的好表現。<ref name="SABR"/><ref name="Sunday Conversation">{{cite web|last=Glover|first=Emery|url=https://thetandd.com/sports/t-d-sunday-conversation-with-bobby-richardson/article_378fc5f2-52ab-11e0-815b-001cc4c03286.html|title=T&D Sunday Conversation with...Bobby Richardson|work=The Times & Democrat|date=2011-03-20|accessdate=2020-04-09|archive-date=2020-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411003623/https://thetandd.com/sports/t-d-sunday-conversation-with-bobby-richardson/article_378fc5f2-52ab-11e0-815b-001cc4c03286.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1961年，雷夫·霍克成為總教練，他開始將理查森放在先發打序的前兩棒。<ref name="SABR"/>該年他全勤出賽162場比賽，打擊率為2成61，並敲出3轟與49分打點。<ref name="reference"/>這年他贏下了金手套獎，而且還在MVP票選上拿下第24名。<ref name="reference"/>

[[1961年世界大賽|1961年世界大賽]]，理查森沒有打回任何打點，不過他的打擊率高達3成91。其中他在第一場和第四場比賽都敲出3支安打，<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>最後洋基4勝1敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。這也是理查森個人的第二冠。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>

1962年6月9日，理查森單場敲出4支安打，包含一支兩分砲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196206090.shtml|title=Baltimore Orioles at New York Yankees Box Score, June 9, 1962|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521061142/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196206090.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也入選了該年度的兩場明星賽。<ref name="reference"/>8月16日，洋基面對參議員以4比7落後時，當時理查森在滿壘時上場打擊。隊友[[米奇·曼托|米奇·曼托]]在理查森上場前還跟他說：「我今天狀況不佳，所以你只要遇到好球就用力地打吧！」<ref name="SABR"/>結果理查森敲出了他在例行賽生涯的唯一一發滿貫砲。而那年他出賽161場比賽，打擊率為3成02，並敲出8轟、59分打點與11次盜壘成功。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1962-batting-leaders.shtml|title=1962 AL Batting Leaders|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2020-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527050456/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1962-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他在MVP票選上僅次於他的隊友曼托。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1962.shtml|title=1962 Awards Voting|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2009-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210033852/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1962.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[1962年世界大賽|1962年世界大賽]]，理查森的打擊率只有1成48。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>不過這年他靠著防守替洋基守下不少分數。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25138329/willie-mccovey-san-francisco-giants-legend-dies-80|title=Willie McCovey, Hall of Famer and Giants legend, dies at age 80|work=ESPN|date=2018-10-31|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2019-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222053425/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25138329/willie-mccovey-san-francisco-giants-legend-dies-80|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中第七戰，洋基當時只有一分領先。巨人隊在9局下半兩出局攻佔二三壘，[[威利·麥考維|威利·麥考維]]擊出強勁平飛球，結果理查森直接將球接進手套，幫助洋基拿下二連霸。<ref name="SABR"/>
===1963年–1966年：生涯後期===
1963年5月，理查森的父親因中風住院，後來他在7月17日去世。而理查森為了處理父親的後事向球隊請了11天的假。<ref name="SABR"/><ref name="Richardson's father">{{cite web|url=https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1963/06/18/80711961.html?pageNumber=37|title=Bobby Richardson's Father, 57|work=The New York Times|date=1963-06-18|accessdate=2020-04-10|page=37|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141432/https://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1963/06/18/80711961.html?pageNumber=37|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年7月初，他曾在3天內兩度達成單場敲出四支安打的成就。<ref name="1963 Richardson"/>他也因此入選了明星賽。<ref name="reference"/>該年他出賽151場比賽，打擊率為2成63，敲出了3轟<ref name="1963 Richardson">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1963|title=Bobby Richardson 1963 Batting Gamelogs|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-18|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417194937/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=richabo01&t=b&year=1963|dead-url=no}}</ref>與48分打點。而他最後在MVP票選上得到第10名，<ref name="reference"/>並拿下[[盧·賈里格紀念獎|盧·賈里格紀念獎]]。<ref name="SABR"/>

1963年世界大賽第一場，理查森吞下了3次三振，這是他例行賽加上季後賽生涯唯一一次單場吞下3次三振。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=richabo01|title=Bobby Richardson Stats|work=Baseball Almanac|accessdate=2020-04-19|archive-date=2020-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613230100/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=richabo01|dead-url=no}}</ref>而道奇隊投手[[山迪·柯法斯|山迪·柯法斯]]也在那場比賽奪下了15次三振，刷新了世界大賽單場三振紀錄。最後洋基在世界大賽被道奇隊橫掃。

1964年6月12日，理查森擊出了生涯第1000支安打。這年他再次入選明星賽。<ref name="reference"/>該年他出賽159場比賽，打擊率為2成67，並敲出4轟、50分打點與11次盜壘成功。<ref name="reference"/>他在MVP票選上拿下第17名。<ref name="reference"/>

1964年世界大賽，理查森一共敲出了13支安打刷新紀錄。這項紀錄只有1968年的[[盧·布羅克|盧·布羅克]]和1986年的{{link-en|馬蒂·巴瑞特|Marty Barrett}}追平而已。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-almanac.com/rb_ws3.shtml|title=World Series Hitting Records|work=Baseball Almanac|accessdate=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611015747/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/rb_ws3.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 雖然他敲出不少安打，但是他到了關鍵時刻還是無法貢獻致命一擊，加上他在第4場和第5場比賽都發生失誤造成球隊失分輸球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196410110.shtml|title=1964 World Series Game 4, Cardinals at Yankees, October 11|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521062701/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196410110.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196410120.shtml|title=1964 World Series Game 5, Cardinals at Yankees, October 12|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521062705/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196410120.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後洋基再次輸掉世界大賽，這也是理查森最後一次參與世界大賽。<ref name="Postseason Richardson"/>

1965年，他出賽160場比賽，打擊率為2成47，並敲出6轟與47分打點。<ref name="reference"/>最後他在MVP票選上拿下第20名。<ref name="reference"/>球季結束時，才30歲的理查森就已打算退休。不過因為[[湯尼·庫貝克|湯尼·庫貝克]]因傷被迫退休，洋基希望理查森可以再打一年。<ref name="SABR"/>1966年9月11日，理查森敲出職業生涯最後一發全壘打。<ref name="SABR"/>該年他出賽149場比賽，留下打擊率2成51，敲出7轟與42分打點的數據。<ref name="reference"/>

球季結束後，理查森表示因為想多陪家人而決定退休，當時他還只有31歲而已。<ref name="Baptist Courier">{{cite web|last=Gray|first=Rudy|url=https://baptistcourier.com/2016/07/christian-faith-marks-yankee-legend-bobby-richardsons-career-home-life/|title=Christian faith marks Yankee legend Bobby Richardson’s career, home life|work=Baptist Courier|date=2016-07-05|accessdate=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930141433/https://baptistcourier.com/2016/07/christian-faith-marks-yankee-legend-bobby-richardsons-career-home-life/|dead-url=no}}</ref>洋基也在9月17日這天訂為理查森日，以表彰他這12年來對洋基的貢獻。
