==1976年眾議院代表選舉==
1974年，美國總統尼克森便嘗試說服理查森代表共和黨參選南卡羅來納州第五選區的眾議員選舉。<ref name="finah">{{cite web|last=Keith|first=Larry|url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1975/06/02/nothin-could-be-finah|title=Nothin', could be finah|work=Sports Illustrated|date=1975-06-02|accessdate=2020-04-17|archive-date=2022-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109104418/https://vault.si.com/vault/1975/06/02/nothin-could-be-finah|dead-url=no}}</ref>2年後，美國總統[[傑拉德·福特|傑拉德·福特]]再次去遊說理查森參選，不過最後理查森以些微差距輸給民主黨的對手[[肯尼斯·荷蘭|肯尼斯·荷蘭]]（Kenneth Holland）。<ref name="The Item">{{cite web|last=Brunson|first=Dennis|url=https://www.theitem.com/stories/the-sumter-items-top-125-sports-figures-no-1-bobby-richardson,338621|title=The Sumter Item's Top 125 Sports Figures: No. 1 - Bobby Richardson|work=The Sumter Item|date=2019-12-26|accessdate=2020-04-20|archive-date=2019-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227224320/https://www.theitem.com/stories/the-sumter-items-top-125-sports-figures-no-1-bobby-richardson,338621|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時理查森還邀請了[[喬·迪馬喬|喬·迪馬喬]]、[[泰德·威廉斯|泰德·威廉斯]]、[[鮑伯·費勒|鮑伯·費勒]]及{{link-en|威爾默·米澤爾|Wilmer Mizell}}幫助他競選，不過前隊友[[湯尼·庫貝克|湯尼·庫貝克]]因為支持民主黨而拒絕為理查森站台。<ref>{{cite book |title=October 1964 |last=Halberstam |first=David |authorlink= |year=1995 |publisher=Random House Digital, Inc. |location= |isbn=0-449-98367-6 |pages=366–367 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sZ7sUkp5eBcC&lpg=PP1&dq=october%201964&pg=PA366#v=onepage&q&f=false |access-date=2020-09-21 |archive-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716230104/https://books.google.com/books?id=sZ7sUkp5eBcC&lpg=PP1&dq=october%201964&pg=PA366#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>
